{"tid":1142510,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"我不難過了, 甚至真心希望你能幸福","createTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T00:18:15.000Z","uid":24754,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65980ba0125b24d11f8e93b771163c3ca39449bf","tid":1142510,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:16:43.000Z","msg":"細佬我就喺度分享一首歌<br />\n蔡健雅 - 陌生人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢首歌有我嘅故仔，其實兩年前已經整咗個底<br />\n但係後來就唔知點解冇繼續整落去<br />\n最近唔覺意打開個folder, 見到未整完嘅歌<br />\n終於的起心肝整咗佢<br />\n<br />\n「一朵雲能載多少思念的寄託，在忽然相遇街頭」<br />\n如果你係街頭撞到未放低嘅「佢」，你會點呢？<br />\n而我已經放低了...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fc8CT7zXxns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFc8CT7zXxns&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=e1681e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fc8CT7zXxns</a>"},{"pid":"bcb4ebf71685001e6ac8c3a32718ed237e40888f","tid":1142510,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f17ff6e6e727f043a83e5262acf5945808dbe6a2","tid":1142510,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n唱得幾好聽<br />\n介唔介意比個簽名小妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a9d3c8583c6c17cf2a0924ed0662cfdb75e67d","tid":1142510,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb4ebf71685001e6ac8c3a32718ed237e40888f","tid":1142510,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"咁都中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b9a59579296ee11c93fcfdb1f1d1e2d77e6a79","tid":1142510,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f17ff6e6e727f043a83e5262acf5945808dbe6a2","tid":11